{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"夜裡，你應當以小部份時間向他叩頭，以大部份時間讚頌他。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"這等人的確愛好現世，而忽視未來的嚴重的一日。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"我創造了他們，並使他們的體格堅實。如果我意欲，我將以像他們一樣的人代替他們。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"這確是教誨，誰願意覺悟，誰可以選擇一條通達他的主的道路。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"除真主意欲外，你們決不意欲。真主是全知的，是至睿的。"},{"SurahNumber":76,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"他使他所意欲的人，入在他的慈恩中。至於不義的人們，他已為他們預備了痛苦的刑罰。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以奉派傳達佳音，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"遂猛烈吹動者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"誓以傳播各物，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"而使之分散，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"乃傳授教訓者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"誓以示原諒或警告者，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"警告你們的事，是必定發生的。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"當星宿黯淡的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"當天體破裂的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"當山巒飛揚的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"當眾使者被定期召集的時候，"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"期限在哪日呢？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"在判決之日。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你怎能知道判決之日，是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"在那日，傷哉否認真理的人們。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"難道我沒有毀滅先民嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"然後，我使後民隨他們而消滅。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"我將這樣處治犯罪的人。"},{"SurahNumber":77,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"在那日，傷哉否認真理的人們。"}]}